    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait a double dose of ibuprofen? how much exactly is \"double\"? like, is it safe to take like 800mg at once if i'm really in pain? and are you sure i don't need an xray right now if it's that bad? i'm just trying to avoid a long wait at the clinic if i can help it.",
